high_descs: Turn around then walk towards the stove, turn left then head towards the wall, then turn and face the garbage can.
Pick up the potato in the garbage can.
Turn around, walk towards the table, turn left then head towards the sink.
Place the potato into the sink then rinse the potato, then turn the water off.
Turn around then head towards the door, turn right then head towards the garbage can.
Place the potato into the garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed potato into the garbage can.

high_descs: Walk to the trash can on the left of the kitchen counter.
Grab the potato from the trash can.
Walk to the kitchen sink on your right.
Place the potato inside the sink and soak it, then grab the potato.
Walk back to the trash can.
Place the potato inside the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Clean off a dirty potato and put it back in the trash.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the trash can
Grab the potato out of the trash can
Turn right and go to the sink
Wash the potato in the sink and then take it out
Turn around and go to the trash can
Put the potato in the trash can
anns.task_desc: Putting a potato in the trash can
